        <text>
            <body>
                <div type="letter">
                <pb facs="#farts_2"/>
                <opener>
                    <salute>Dear<persName ref="#mother">mother</persName>!</salute>
               </opener>
               <p>For a long time I didn't received letters from You, and I am really worried. 
                  Recently I received the money from uncle <persName ref="#uncle">Jacob</persName>. 
                  There are no other news and I don't know where to send letters. I still live in the same
                  <placeName ref="#camp">camp</placeName> with the same conditions of life. 
                  It's hard, but I'm armed with my patience. I am well. Nothing new. 
                  From brothers <persName ref="#brother_nikolay">Nikolay</persName>and
                  <persName ref="#brother_georgy">Georgiy</persName> I also haven't any news and 
                  I don't know where and how they live.
                </p>
               <closer>
                    <signed>Your son<persName ref="#Ivan_Farts">Ivan</persName></signed>
               </closer>
               </div>   
            </body>
